MUSI 424: Senior Recital. 1 credit.
Public recital by student during senior year. Notes: Senior recital must be at least 50 minutes long. All recitals by arrangement. Students must consult with director of applied music studies to register and schedule dates. Offered by Dewberry School of Music. Limited to three attempts.
Mason Core: Capstone
